  VERSION=( "1.04" "0.9.1" )
 CATEGORY="library"
ATTRIBUTE="new library"
   SOURCE="pme-$VERSION"
 HOMEPAGE="http://xaxxon.slackworks.com/pme"
      URL="$HOMEPAGE"
    SHORT="C++ bindings for pcre"
      REQ="pcre"
 ESTIMATE="29"
FRESHMEAT="pme"
     LONG="
PME is a C++ wrapper around the PCRE library. It has been designed to
emulate Perl regular expression in both syntax and behaviour. PME requires
PCRE version 4.3+ be installed.
"